1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 4.1-01 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to creating a farm management program within the department of
3 agriculture; to amend and reenact section 15-20.1-03 of the North Dakota Century Code,
4 relating to the powers and duties of the state board of career at technical education; and to
5 provide an appropriation.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
7 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 4.1-01 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
8 and enacted as follows:
9 Farm management program.
10 The commissioner shall implement and oversee a program to:
11 1. Coordinate new and existing farm management programs offered by a state agency,
12 board, or commission; and
13 2. Create and expand marketing clubs as adjuncts to new and existing farm
14 management programs.
15 SECTION 2. AMENDMENT. Section 15-20.1-03 of the North Dakota Century Code is
16 amended and reenacted as follows:
17 15-20.1-03. Powers and duties of state board relating to career and technical
18 education.
19 The state board shall have all authority necessary to cooperate with the United States
20 department of education or other department or agency of the United States of America in the
21 administration of acts of Congress relating to career and technical education, including the
22 following powers and duties:
23 1. To administer any legislation enacted by the legislative assembly of this state pursuant
24 to or in conformity with acts of Congress relating to career and technical education.
